    {
      "para_id": "Q001581.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) To Bau , the kind woman , child of An , lady of Iri-kug , her lady , Ninkagina , her house-born slave , dedicated this ( female statuette with the name : ) “Whenever the protective spirit of Tarsirsir enters the courtyard of Bau , this statue will attract my lady's attention towards him . May it pray to her on my behalf!” as an offering for the well-being of Nammaḫni , ruler of Lagaš ."
    }
  ],
